  "description": "忘却前夜是一款克苏鲁题材改编的Roguelite卡牌构筑游戏。玩家扮演守密人，链接游走在疯狂边缘的唤醒体，构筑专属策略牌组，探索迷雾地图、遭遇随机事件，调查这世界正在死去的真相。",
  "description_en": "Morimens is a roguelite card-building game inspired by the Cthulhu mythos. Players craft versatile decks, explore misty maps, encounter random events, and uncover the truth of a dying world.",
